xt-indent: -18.4pt; line-height: 25.6pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"> </p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 18.4pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.4pt; line-height: 25.6pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"> 바. 문의처 </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 18.4pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.4pt; line-height: 25.6pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   - 첨부 공고문 및 FAQ를 먼저 읽고 문의할 것 </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 18.4pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.4pt; line-height: 25.6pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   - 접수 관련: 글로벌교류팀 02-2260-3464 / outbound1@dongguk.edu</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 18.4pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.4pt; line-height: 25.6pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   - 사업 관련(지원자격, 장학혜택 등): 한국산업기술진흥원 02-6009-3225, threesseul@kiat.or.kr</span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 18.4pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: -18.4pt; line-height: 25.6pt; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 바탕;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:tahoma;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative;\">   </span></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"HStyle0\" style=\"margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 114pt; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; text-indent: